00:26:02.660 --> 00:26:03.620
¡Maldita sea!

897
00:26:03.620 --> 00:26:04.620
¡Es fuerte!

898
00:26:07.120 --> 00:26:09.540
¡Alcaide Babanuki!

899
00:26:09.540 --> 00:26:12.130
